item.title: CVE-2023-6627|2024-01-08T19:00:30.023Z -- unknown -- wp%20go%20maps%20%28formerly%20wp%20google%20maps%29
item.description: The WP Go Maps (formerly WP Google Maps) WordPress plugin before 9.0.28 does not properly protect most of its REST API routes, which attackers can abuse to store malicious HTML/Javascript on the site.
